  "description": "A surreal Lovecraftian cosmic horror creature. The main body is an asymmetric, floating polyhedron crystalline cluster made of iridescent, semi-translucent obsidian glass that shifts between deep violet and oily teal. Projecting outward from the non-Euclidean facets are twelve elongated, jointed spider-like appendages, but instead of joints, the limbs are connected by hovering, unattached glowing magenta energy rings. Each limb terminates in a finely detailed human hand pointing outward in a stiff, radial pattern. At the epicenter of the crystalline cluster is a massive, wet mammalian eye with an inverted, horizontal goat-like pupil, surrounded by a ring of twitching, fleshy cilia instead of eyelids. Drooping from the bottom of the central mass are several thin, dangling sea-anemone tentacles with micro-sucker textures.",
